description.narrative: Output 1 Indicators: Publication and utilization of existing and future guidance documents. Output 2 Indicator: a) Number of training workshops/activities carried out, b) Number of targeted backstopping activities carried out. Output 3 Indicator: Partnership between public and private sectors to address mitigation actions in selected industries. Output 4 Targets: Coordinated production and dissemination of lessons learned and knowledge products

comment.narrative: Output 1 Baseline: Tools and guidance material not readily utilized. Output 2 Baseline: Limited technical support and training activities on NAMA, LEDS and MRV. Output 3 Baseline: An absence of partnerships between public and private sectors in the realm of low emission/mitigation actions. Output 4 Baseline: Dissemination of knowledge products and lessons learned conducted in an ad-hoc manner.
